        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/edb3f5/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-07-14T15:43:20.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Interesting article in today\u2019s NYTimes by Eric:<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/13/dining/wine-review-montepulciano-d-abruzzo.html?hpw&amp;rref=food&amp;action=click&amp;pgtype=Homepage&amp;module=well-region&amp;region=bottom-well&amp;WT.nav=bottom-well\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Montepulciano d\u2019Abruzzo</a></p>\n<p>I didn\u2019t realize there were any priced above $100/btl. Slathered w/ new Fr.oak I gather. Sigh!!</p>\n<p>The NYTimes headline doesn\u2019t reflect the subject matter very well.<br>\nTom</p>",
