        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/8797f3/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-07-14T18:50:42.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Recently had a 2015 La Quercia Montepulciano d\u2019Abruzzo for $10 that was one of the best wines I\u2019ve ever drunk at that price point. Juicy, medium-bodied, very authentic.</p>",
